ED.getValue()),\\n            SampleComEnum.class,\\n            null,\\n            false,\\n            false\\n        );\\n\\n        assertThat(result).isEqualTo(SampleComEnum.SELECTED);\\n    }\\n\\n    private static Class<?> convertClass() throws ClassNotFoundException {\\n        return Class.forName(\\\"com.sun.jna.platform.win32.COM.util.Convert\\\");\\n    }\\n\\n    public enum SampleComEnum implements IComEnum {\\n        IGNORED(11),\\n        SELECTED(42);\\n\\n        private final long value;\\n\\n        SampleComEnum(long value) {\\n            this.value = value;\\n        }\\n\\n        @Override\\n        public long getValue() {\\n            return value;\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777525500534}, {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_iczC1tQFN8BInWzw9GjB3rOC|fc_03c664e97a67160b0169f2e2facbc081a28b61e8159464a583\", \"toolName\": \"read\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage net_java_dev_jna.jna_platform;\\n\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\\n\\npublic class Jna_platformTest {\\n    @Test\\n    void test() throws Exception {\\n        System.out.println(\\\"This is just a placeholder, implement your test\\\");\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777525500534}]}\nhuman-intervention-logs/net.java.dev.jna:jna-platform:5.8.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-30T05-06-03-802289Z.log:1764:       *                     value is DISP_E_TYPEMISMATCH or DISP_E_PARAMNOTFOUND. This argument can be set to null. For details, see Returning Errors.\nhuman-intervention-logs/net.java.dev.jna:jna-platform:5.8.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-30T05-06-03-802289Z.log:1779:       * One of the arguments in DISPPARAMS could not be co